Class RealSubstanceService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.RealSubstanceService

  • public class RealSubstanceService
extends Object

    With this service, you can read real substance attributes, such as header data or composition via an OData service.
